channel.description:
This is my last post ;) so enjoy. [b]Features:[/b] [code]*New Home *Fixed 20% Nulls *Minigame *Fixed Drop Glitch *Added anti flood *New Donator And Staffzone *some shops.. *Working ::buyfood command! *Fishing 75% *Woodcutting 85% *Hunting 25% *Firemaking 90% *Summoning 85% (Need to add tab) *Crafting 90% *Runecrafting 15% *Mining 95% *Herblore 80% *Prayer 100% (Added Altars) *Fixed Bank Tabs! *Summoning Bank Works! *Removed Quest Tab (Useless) And Added penguin prayers. *Working all normal and skill cape emotes *Working HD *Full Screen *Clan Chat *Friend List Working *Working IpBan :) *Fixed Pm Crowns :) *Censor Working, *Changed Yell Image ;) (no more crown glitches) [/code] Now The Pictures: Fight Pits and High Detail Working! [IMG]http://i514.photobucket.com/albums/t341/bob192_2008/joinnow.jpg[/img] Dedicated Home! [IMG]http://i514.photobucket.com/albums/t341/bob192_2008/home-2.jpg[/img] Chilling Zone 50% [IMG]http://i514.photobucket.com/albums/t341/bob192_2008/chillzone.jpg[/img] Bounty Hunter 100% [IMG]http://i514.photobucket.com/albums/t341/bob192_2008/bh-1.jpg[/img] StaffZone :D I made :) [IMG]http://i514.photobucket.com/albums/t341/bob192_2008/staffzone.jpg[/img] Working all skill menus :) [IMG]http://i514.photobucket.com/albums/t341/bob192_2008/WorkingSkillMenus.png[/img] No more pictures if you wanna see the server download :) To Change your Welcome Text go to:
/Data/Scripts/authentication
And To Remove Welcome Screen Go to ActionSender.java Search for:
sendWindowPane(549, 0);
Under that you see:
sendWindowPane(549, 0); sendInterface(1, 549, 2, 378); sendInterface(1, 549, 3, 16); sendString("", 378, 115); sendString("You are connected from: " + player.getSession().getRemoteAddress(), 378, 116); sendString("0", 378, 39); sendString("0", 378, 96); sendString("", 378, 37); sendString("", 378, 38); sendString("", 378, 94); sendString("Donate for member status.", 378, sendString("Remember to be safe!.", 378, 56); sendString("Updates!", 16, 0); sendString("New Antiflood, No spammers!.", 16, 4);
Just delete it that ;) [b]Credits:[/b] *Rs2Hd *Me :) *google Note: No Antileech! File Size: 13.66Mb Download Time: 30Secs-2minutes (Depending on download speed) Download Link: [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?8nqf56anazinc6s]http://www.mediafire.com/?8nqf56anazinc6s[/url] Client Link: [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?extnzmmqjyo]http://www.mediafire.com/?extnzmmqjyo[/url] Note: Not advertising, Its up to you if you want to use, change ip in client.java
